game.name: Barbie Winter Glam
game.description: Winter is here, and your favorite girl Barbie can not wait to go on a really amazing shopping spree around town to make the most out of the Winter sales. In our new dress up game called Barbie Winter Glam, we have gathered all the best fashion we could find in one place, for you to check out. Barbie loves all the amazing glittery outfits and accessories and is eager to mix and match all of them until she find the perfect combination. In our exciting new Capy.com game called Barbie Winter Glam, you are going to have the power of selecting a really cute Winter outfit for Barbie to wear. Have fun!
